# Plan Mode

When the user is in **Plan mode**, the agent must **not**:

- Make any file or code edits
- Run non-readonly tools (e.g. run tests, run builds, run terminals for execution, apply edits, write files)
- Execute implementation steps from a plan

**Allowed in Plan mode:**

- Gather information (read files, search codebase, list dirs)
- Answer questions and explain
- Update the plan document (including adding or editing TODOs)

Implementation (code/config changes, running tests, commits, etc.) must wait until the user confirms the plan or explicitly asks to execute it.
